title: Episode 32: Shari Sees Gender as a Gift
description: Today I have a wonderful conversation featuring my friend Shari. Shari is a Canadian farmer who has wisdom to share on a whole host of topics, but today she shares her thoughts on gender and what it means to be masculine and feminine and how embrace those roles can ultimately be a gift to others. I truly enjoyed her impute and I hope you do too!
